Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇部的海報 做得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會有點過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的 挺帥氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼感想？ 凱瑟琳學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也畫成這麼美的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是本劇招牌女演員的評論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎學姐本來就很美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說啦 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會有剩下能帶走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帖在房間裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小井 是不是低了點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠帶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實場排練快要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也快一點帖完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了嗎？ 那個招搖的海報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 挺漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本學姐 那個海報如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 畫成了那個樣子 感覺有點惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 學姐本人還要……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那……那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她說上話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底和她到底說了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密 保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐被大家所愛慕著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 妒嫉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠近一點還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點懷疑學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人是否另有其人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一這麼想就停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就變得無法交談了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然也不清楚這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人說過 喜歡伴隨著不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是這樣對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧平同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁要喝點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來問問大家要什麼 部長叫我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 在這
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧平同學 希斯克裏夫的手杖…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 壞掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 井汲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 那你要點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就橙汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬 待會見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬城目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝點什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉 讓你來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的人是杉本學姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本學姐真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡她的人也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK 大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥氣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 回去路上小心一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是京子啊 真是有心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年級生要開會 到這集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一、二年級生收拾完了就可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會忙到很晚 你先回去也可以哦 富美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了 杉本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼從第75頁的對白開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不跟學姐一起回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她說可能會忙到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 要去喝茶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位無所謂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學 和富美一起也行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我喜歡的人的話 到哪我都會帶著她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在在鐮倉車站附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和小晶她們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給家裏打電話 還真是老實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是富美醬是個好孩子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐是喜歡那孩子對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直都誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我等你」我還以為你會這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想要說的話就要說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 富美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好在意 都睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和井汲京子同學談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說喜歡學姐你 然後就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 富美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得初戀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個喜歡上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美醬 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼好事情對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢 昨天學姐打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得初戀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的初戀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲劇祭的出演者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有工作人員以外的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在放學後離校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還缺點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把花朵弄分散一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學部是演什麼戲來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小王子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子演的是小王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性的花是誰演呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏 小心台階
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要撞上 很容易壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在試演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 杉本學姐在哪裏知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐還沒來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來能遇上呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 因為試演在小學部的後面 所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在不在 等下再說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼幫著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 奧平同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物來了我不怕 因為我有荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走 不是已經決定要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒想到過兩人喜歡著對方 但還是有人會悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我逃出來就是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這麼愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這就是她的溫柔之處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美不去的話 我也不怎麼想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐不是主角嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思和京子見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不好意思…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她可是還經常見面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐是被叫去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想叫富美去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用這樣的聲調 我也……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美在同情她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 今天就一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好厲害 這個是京子織的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人怎麼可能 是和這裏的大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好厲害 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本來就是我們工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 喜歡甜的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 這麼難得就大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個打算的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種人氣 難怪富美會不好意思來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那我們去借盤子和叉子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好厲害哦 京子 是親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 能不能站一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶要不要來吃蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假縫線先就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有動起來不方便的地方的話說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果富美在的話就拜託她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井汲同學也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶 真有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個看這個 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣用手抱著腰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著的地方好下流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個這個 好厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的上演的時候會不會接吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 紅茶 紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不是真的喜歡才鬧成那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就不是這樣……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我還有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能算是FAN裏的一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是同那些女孩一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是對我說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏只有學姐和我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前京子說的 和過去一樣相處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要只看字面意思 我只是在逞強罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣直接說出來才像京子 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妹妹一樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都放不下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子是個好孩子 不會鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有點想見富美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詢問處？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 戲劇祭的會場的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經拜託部長了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼做富美不是都不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒這事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我叫你 你就來咯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷不？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子很新鮮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別作弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 富美醬直接說出來多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯過開口時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是吃醋罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很好嘛 才是少女心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之那種人不直接跟她挑明的話可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她明說「請別隨便玩弄我的感情」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那不是有點奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也在擔心富美是不是不來 我好高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的戲劇祭 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成功就太好了
